Actress Funke Akindele has revealed her twins are Zack and Zion. The actress has always been so protective of their identities since they were born. She said that she wanted them to enjoy life without the cons of fame because they are still kids.   My dress costs $100,000 – Ifu Ennada     Omoni Oboli, touts at war over movie production     Audition for BBNaija Season 7 begins   However, her husband JJSkillz’s baby mama, in anger revealed the faces of the children after alleging they maltreated her son Benito. Funke, while receiving an award at the AMVCA for her movie Omo Ghetto, did not spare to make them known as part of the reasons she’s grateful. She said: “Thank you so much my fans, my family, my siblings, my husband, my beautiful children – Zack and Zion – I dedicate this to all the cast and crew of Omo Ghetto The Saga. I want to say something briefly, no matter what you face in life, do not forget your purpose, challenges will come. I shot Omoghetto during my drama with Covid, I stayed focused and today I got it”.